::Rex::

Rex frowns, looking at Battera. "What faction is this Voluis?"

If Voluis was a Predacon, it was almost definite that it was some sort of 
trap. Predacons were not ussually peaceful. He waits for her answer, 
wondering if Kluster would rist a 'peace meeting' sponsored by Predacons.
